h2. Examples

The following are the examples located in the example directory. Note that
<ruby>
require File.dirname(__FILE__) + '/example_helper'
</ruby>
should be replaced with 
<ruby>
require 'rubygems'
require 'gecoder'
</ruby>
when running them from another location.

